and listen.

04:21.350 --> 04:23.480
Now, when I shot you, you were
trying to give me a password.

04:23.510 --> 04:24.550
Right?

04:24.580 --> 04:25.780
- Blue.
- So I... yeah.

04:25.820 --> 04:27.750
